Package: metadid
Title: Bayesian Meta-Analysis Across Study Designs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ben", "Lambert", email = "ben.c.lambert@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Bayesian meta-analysis framework for synthesizing treatment 
    effects across different study designs, including difference-in-differences 
    (DiD), randomized controlled trials (RCT), and pre-post designs. Implements 
    hierarchical models in Stan that account for design-specific biases, missing 
    correlation structures, and heterogeneity across studies.
